{"tid":748650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖估國家）人妻輕鐵熊抱... 竟在列車上脫光衣服！","createTime":"2018-07-19T11:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T16:10:25.000Z","uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"033eb40219ed43ab81564623d31f2efd825d9a44","tid":748650,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/192128_d1a49e78842092b093bb47df60c61902.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F192128_d1a49e78842092b093bb47df60c61902.png&h=a1a11376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四川渠縣今日下午有一名36歲女子，疑因與丈夫出現感情問題導致情緒失控，在輕鐵列車上如同樹熊般撲向一名56歲男乘客，把對方咬傷。男乘客血流披面忍痛逃脫後，涉事女子竟在列車上脫光衣服，開始伏在地舔着該名男乘客滴下的血漬，其他乘客見狀嚇得「雞飛狗走」，情景如同南韓電影《屍殺列車》的混亂場面。<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180718&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58458520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180718%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58458520&d=124IUb7iGtHz3%2FubD%2B6YjG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fe681950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180718%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58458520&h=6535ffbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180718&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58458520</a><br />\n【似屍殺列車】人妻輕鐵熊抱噬咬陌生男 仲剝光豬舔地上血漬<br />\n<br />\n我發現冇人post大陸負面新聞架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8b597683f854b2a460b2e63827733962bc91bb","tid":748650,"uid":157535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"開始伏在地舔着該名男乘客滴下的血漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor